<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= pkg.name %></title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="<%= css %>" media="all" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>File Reading</h1>
    <ol>
      <li>use the file selector to show the chosen image in the `div#viewer` element</li>
      <li>enable dragging and dropping an image onto the viewer instead of using file input</li>
      <li>give the viewer element some style to indicate it's a droppable target</li>
    </ol>

    <main>
      <div id="viewer"></div>
      <input type=file />
    </main>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="<%= js %>"></script>
  </body>
</html>
